description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Annie Taylor performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 6, 2023. 

Songs:
Midnight
Love is Blind
Figure it Out
Where the Grass is Greener
Wasted Youth

Gini Jungi - Vocals, Guitar
Tobias Arn - Guitar
Michael Mutter - Bass, 
Daniel Bachmann - Drums, Vocals

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Guest Audio Engineer: Jerome Longhi
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Carlos Cruz
